r: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family\" times new roman font-size: font-style: normal font-variant-caps: letter-spacing: orphans: auto text-align: start text-indent: text-transform: none white-space: pre widows: word-spacing: rgba text-decoration:>          </b>Resilient...\n\n(turns to Ariadne)\n\nHighly contagious, and an idea can\n\ngrow. The smallest seed of an idea\n\ncan grow to define or destroy your\n\nworld...\n\n<b style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family\" times new roman font-size: font-style: normal font-variant-caps: letter-spacing: orphans: auto text-align: start text-indent: text-transform: none white-space: pre widows: word-spacing: rgba text-decoration:></b>\n\nCobb is staring into the kitchen. Mal is sitting at the\n\ntable, back to them, staring out at the porch- the TOWERS of\n\nLimbo stretching off behind it.        <b style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family\" times new roman font-size: font-style: normal font-variant-caps: letter-spacing: orphans: auto text-align: start text-indent: text-transform: none white-space: pre widows: word-spacing: rgba text-decoration:>             </b>\n\n<b style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family\" times new roman font-size: font-style: normal font-variant-caps: letter-spacing: orphans: auto text-align: start text-indent: text-transform: none white-space: pre widows: word-spacing: rgba text-decoration:></b>\n\n<b style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family\" times new roman font-size: font-style: normal font-variant-caps: letter-spacing: orphans: auto text-align: start text-indent: text-transform: none white-space: pre widows: word-spacing: rgba text-decoration:>                    MAL</b>\n\n<b style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family\" times new roman font-size: font-style: normal font-variant-caps: letter-spacing: orphans: auto text-align: start text-indent: text-transform: none white-spa